  "remarks": "Tunisian passport number: L851940, issued on 9 September 1998, expired on 8 September 2003. Sentenced to six years of imprisonment for international terrorism in 2008. Deported from Italy to Tunisia on 10 Feb 2013. Inadmissible to the Schengen area. Mother’s name is Khadijah al-Drissi. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 22 Apr. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.; Listing: Listed by the UN 1267 Committee on 12 November 2003 (amended on 20 December 2005 and 31 July 2006, 21 Dec 2007, 16 May 2011, 6 Dec 2019, 10 Sep 2020)",
